            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, roughly tear your<strong> chestnut mushrooms</strong> into the pan</p><p>Add your <strong>hoisin sauce</strong> and <strong>soy sauce</strong> and cook for 3-4 min further until everything is combined and the mushrooms have started to soften and the pork is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1674550101645-x200.jpg",
