        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the mushrooms have softened, stir through the <strong>shredded lettuce </strong>and<strong> toasted sesame seeds</strong> – this is your <strong>hoisin lean pork & mushrooms</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1674550110682-x200.jpg",
