            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1674550110682-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>lettuce leaves </strong>to the side of your bowl and top with the <strong>cooked brown rice </strong>and <strong>hoisin lean pork & mushrooms</strong></p><p>Garnish with your <strong>crispy onions </strong>and<strong> chilli rounds </strong>(can’t handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Tip: Make loaded lettuce cups by adding filling to the<strong> </strong>lettuce leaves!</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
